CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 14, 1959, pg. 21, reads: "...guests at the annual Dapper Dan dinner Sunday night at the Hotel Penn Sheraton. Others in picture are Jim Brown, Cleveland Browns' fullback.... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Dr. Charles Bookert, Cleveland Browns football player Jim Brown, and Pittsburgh Courier newspaper editor Bill Nunn Sr., seated in Penn Sheraton Hotel for Dapper Dan banquet
